name: Prevea Health
notes: Physician-owned, 501(c)(3) nonprofit multispecialty group practice with 200+ physicians across 60+ specialties and 50+ locations. Partners with HSHS hospitals but is independently owned and governed.

name: Group Health Cooperative of South Central Wisconsin
notes: Member-owned nonprofit cooperative (501(c)(3)) operating multiple clinics in the Madison area with employed physicians. Staff-model HMO founded in 1972 serving 70,000+ members.

name: Olmsted Medical Center
notes: Independent, physician-led 501(c)(3) nonprofit multispecialty group practice with 290+ clinicians across 35+ specialties and 25+ locations in southeastern Minnesota. Also operates a 61-bed community hospital.
